A Studio Ghibli style illustration of a young Asian student sitting on a grassy hilltop at sunset, releasing dozens of colorful paper origami cranes into a warm golden sky. The cranes transform and dissolve into streams of light as they rise higher. Below the hill, a bustling city with distinctive Singapore-inspired architecture glows softly in the evening light. The student's expression is peaceful and determined, looking upward with hope. Soft clouds drift by in painterly brushstrokes, with rich amber, coral, and lavender tones blending across the sky. Delicate wildflowers sway in the foreground, and a gentle wind animates the scene with movement and life. The atmosphere conveys themes of youth, choice, hope, and personal freedom.
